=== 百年看台/特雷弗·布鲁金爵士看台 ===
[[File:CentenaryStandBG.JPG|250px]]
特雷弗·布鲁金爵士看台在1995年、時逢自1895年所成立的{{link-en|泰晤士河鐵工廠足球會|Thames Ironworks F.C.}}後一百週年時而興建，上下分為兩層，共有6,000個座位。上層為家庭看台，需要帶一名小孩進場方可購買此層門票。原名为百年看台，为了表彰[[特雷弗·布鲁金|特雷弗·布鲁金]]对球队的突出贡献，自2009年8月8日起，百年看台正式更名为特雷弗·布鲁金爵士看台<ref>[http://www.whufc.com/page/News/0,,12562~1727112,00.html Stand For Sir Trevor] {{Wayback|url=http://www.whufc.com/page/News/0,,12562~1727112,00.html |date=20090724154238 }} www.whufc.com</ref>。

=== 東看台 ===
[[File:West_Ham_match_Boleyn_Ground_2006.jpg|250px]]
東看台於1965年興建，座落於球場之遠處，電視攝影機的對面。這個看台是球場內最殘舊及最小。

=== 南看台/卜比·摩亞看台 ===
卜比·摩亞看台（南看台）在1993年興建，有9,000個座位，以滿足英足總對職業球會的球場所訂的新規管。看台的命名為紀念在興建當年逝世，球隊在1960年代中期興盛時期的傳奇隊長[[卜比·摩亞|卜比·摩亞]]（Bobby Moore）。看台共有兩層，每層的坐位顏色砌成韋斯咸的[[英文|英文]]名稱「''{{lang|en|WEST HAM UNITED}}''」橫貫整個看台。下層看台與百年看台一樣主要供熱情的主場球迷進場觀戰，站立及高歌支持主隊。在上層與下職之間設有行政廂房，同時亦設置一個數字時計。看台於2001年馬丁大夫看台落成後曾作小規模翻新，在兩座看台之間設置第二座[[LCD|LCD]]屏幕，更在連接的角落增加坐位。

=== 西看台/馬汀大夫看台 ===
[[File:Boleyn_Ground_Upton_Park_2.jpg|250px]]
[[馬汀大夫|馬汀大夫]]看台（西看台）建於2001年，是球場內最新興建及擁有15,000個座位的看台。球場座位數目由26,000個提升至35,647個，是烏普頓公園球場的主看台，設有兩層看台供購票入座的主場球迷，在兩層看台之間置有兩層行政廂房，而球會的辦公室、董事會室、套房、更衣室、精品店、球會博物館及全新的韋斯咸酒店（West Ham United Hotel）全部在這座建築物內。它亦是[[倫敦|倫敦]]內最大的單一足球場看台，在看台外牆建有兩座別具特色的巨型塔樓，其上各鑲嵌有球會的會徵。看台兩端分別連接百年看台及卜比·摩亞看台的角落設有積分板，顯示即時比數及比賽時間。

2009年赞助合同结束后改回“西看台”的旧称。<ref>[http://www.whufc.com/page/News/0,,12562~1693261,00.html Season tickets selling well]  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090619023642/http://www.whufc.com/page/News/0%2C%2C12562~1693261%2C00.html |date=19 June 2009  }} – whufc.com</ref>

== 門票 ==
韋斯咸把在英超聯比賽日門票分為A類及B類，兩類的比賽定價不同。A類比賽主要是迎戰[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]、[[切尔西足球俱乐部|車路士]]、[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]、[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]及[[熱刺|熱刺]]，票價較高。而其餘十四隊的比賽則為B類，票價較低。

十六歲以下的支持者可以在一賽季享用三次「''{{lang|en|Kids For A Quid}}''」特別優惠，只需用[[英镑|£]]1購買門票便可進場。韋斯咸青少年球迷會（''{{lang|en|Junior Hammers Club}}''）會員，每個賽季可獲得兩場JHC會員比賽的免費門票。

== 拆除 ==
球场在2016年以4000万英镑价格出售，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://landregistry.data.gov.uk/app/ppd|title=Land registry price paid data search: enter postcode E13 9AZ|date=2016-07-15|publisher=Land Registry|access-date=2017-01-10|archive-date=2022-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220404132357/https://landregistry.data.gov.uk/app/ppd/|dead-url=no}}</ref>开发商计划于2018年建成838户住宅、零售店和休闲设施，并透露了建造鲍比摩尔雕像和以他命名的景观花园的可能性。但该计划因只包含51套“保障性住房”（affordable housing）而引起争议<ref name="2016plus">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-26119697|title=West Ham agree Upton Park sale deal with Galliard Group|date=2014-02-10|work=BBC News|access-date=2014-02-11|archive-date=2019-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204001402/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-26119697|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="eveningstandard">{{cite web|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/news/london/plan-for-west-hams-ground-breaks-council-rules-as-upton-park-village-to-have-no-social-housing-10084156.html|title=Plan for West Ham's ground 'breaks council rules' as Upton Park 'village' to have no social housing|last1=Blunden|first1=Mark|publisher=London Evening Standard|access-date=2015-03-16|archive-date=2018-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613111502/https://www.standard.co.uk/news/london/plan-for-west-hams-ground-breaks-council-rules-as-upton-park-village-to-have-no-social-housing-10084156.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。后来开发商将“保障性住房”的比例提高到25%<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.newhamrecorder.co.uk/news/boleyn_ground_development_approved_with_minimum_of_25_affordable_housing_1_4452551|title=Boleyn Ground development approved with minimum of 25% affordable housing|author=Mayhew, Freddy|date=2016-03-11|work=Newham Recorder|access-date=2016-03-15|archive-date=2017-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170325204425/http://www.newhamrecorder.co.uk/news/boleyn_ground_development_approved_with_minimum_of_25_affordable_housing_1_4452551|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年3月，球场拆除工作开始，球场的大门被移走，用于[[伦敦奥林匹克体育场|伦敦奥林匹克体育场]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.whufc.com/News/Articles/2016/March/14-March/Gates-start-journey-to-new-home|title=Gates start journey to new home|publisher=www.whufc.com|access-date=2016-03-15|archive-date=2016-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315141445/http://www.whufc.com/News/Articles/2016/March/14-March/Gates-start-journey-to-new-home|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月，座椅拆卸完毕。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.claretandhugh.info/boleyn-ground-boarded-up/|title=Boleyn Ground boarded up - Claretandhugh|access-date=2016-07-18|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227150515/https://www.claretandhugh.info/boleyn-ground-boarded-up/|dead-url=no}}</ref>8月，球场所有权移交给[[邦瑞地产|邦瑞地产]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/sport/football/boleyn-grounds-east-stand-knocked-down-as-demolition-work-continues-at-west-hams-former-home-a3416956.html|title=Boleyn Ground's East Stand knocked down as demolition work continues|last=Bhardwaj|first=Vaishali|date=2016-12-09|newspaper=Evening Standard|access-date=2017-11-17|archive-date=2017-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117122540/https://www.standard.co.uk/sport/football/boleyn-grounds-east-stand-knocked-down-as-demolition-work-continues-at-west-hams-former-home-a3416956.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月28日，博林球场举办了一场慈善赛，随后开始了拆除工作。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/sport/football/boleyn-ground-demolition-begins-after-upton-park-hosts-final-football-match-a3355406.html|title=Boleyn Ground demolition begins after Upton Park hosts final match|date=2016-09-28|work=London Evening Standard|accessdate=2021-09-06|archive-date=2021-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210906065814/https://www.standard.co.uk/sport/football/boleyn-ground-demolition-begins-after-upton-park-hosts-final-football-match-a3355406.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>球场的部分砖头被出售给球迷供纪念。<ref>{{cite news |first=Hayley |last=Anderson |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/stories-4988420 |title='I'm proud my son is storing 1,000 bricks in my garden' |work=BBC News |date=2019-10-12 }}{{Dead link}}</ref>2018年9月，球场基本拆除完毕。<ref>{{cite news |author1=Tom Farmery |title=Pictured: 112 years of history reduced to a block of flats… how Upton Park has been transformed since West Ham's move to the London Stadium |url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-6160449/Pictured-112-years-history-reduced-block-flats-Upton-Park-transformed.html |accessdate=2021-09-06 |work=每日电讯报 |date=2018-09-12 |archive-date=2021-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210906064001/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-6160449/Pictured-112-years-history-reduced-block-flats-Upton-Park-transformed.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

